 Syntax  &lt;img class=&quot;img-fluid&quot; src=&quot;img_chania.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Chania&quot;&gt;  BS_Spacing: my  Description   Assign responsive-friendly margin or padding values to an element or a subset of its sides with shorthand classes
 Syntax  &lt;div class=&quot;my&quot;&gt; Centered element &lt;/div&gt;

String str.includes()
// true or false 를 반환한다. // if 문에 넣어 쓴다. let str = 'To be, or not to be, that is the question.'; console.log(str.includes('To be')); // true console.log(str.includes('question')); // true console.log(str.includes('nonexistent')); // false console.log(str.includes('To be', 1)); // false console.log(str.includes('TO BE')); // false console.log(str.includes(''))  str.match(regexp)
